snippet.title: Sailor Moon S: Jougai Rantou!? Shuyaku Soudatsusen Japanese Commercial
snippet.description:
Sailor Moon S: Jougai Rantou!? Shuyaku Soudatsusen was one of several Sailor Moon 2D fighters released during the 90s. Whether you're into the anime or not, a Sailor Moon fighter is just plain cool!

Visit chrislovesjapan.com for more content.

My transcription of the audio:
激しく、美しく。
今、戦士達の闘いが始まり！
果たして、最強の戦士は誰なのか?
セーラームーン　スーパー 場外乱闘！？主役争奪戦
